nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Good afternoon,     Please call our office at XXX-XXX-XXXX to schedule these appts. You will need to get the portflushed in Org1 but the secretaries can help schedule that as well-Org1 is only doing port flushes for patients receiving chemo that day. Stay warm and safe in the snow!
